These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
2 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, yellow
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person driving the helicopter is the person who growsazalea##1
6. the social-worker is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea        | hot-chocolate |
| Game          | mah-jongg  | canasta     |
| Flower         | azalea    | bellflower         |
| Job           | analyst    | social-worker |
| Color   | emerald  | yellow     |
| Cigar           | pall-mall      | aristoff    |
| Transport         | helicopter | jet-ski          |

